521
00:44:22,147 --> 00:44:29,547

522
00:44:34,767 --> 00:44:37,007
- Aiyoo.
- Aiyoo.

523
00:44:39,767 --> 00:44:46,787
So we fervently fought to do the Prime Minister's surgery but then BAM the hospital's been eliminated from the outside!

