543
00:46:11,917 --> 00:46:14,187
So come here and handle the leftovers.

544
00:46:18,427 --> 00:46:20,367
Are you mad?

545
00:46:22,167 --> 00:46:27,577
Well, I was a little sad after you left like that.

546
00:46:29,067 --> 00:46:32,287
