550
00:46:43,497 --> 00:46:46,067
Ah, I see.

551
00:46:47,367 --> 00:46:49,097
Why Doctor Park?

552
00:46:49,097 --> 00:46:50,947
No.

553
00:46:50,947 --> 00:46:56,797
Doctor Han made some curry, I mean food, and there are a lot of leftovers.

554
00:46:56,797 --> 00:46:58,297
I'll call you back after I ask him.

555
00:46:58,297 --> 00:47:00,807
Okay.

556
00:47:06,297 --> 00:47:07,507
What happened?

557
00:47:07,507 --> 00:47:09,977
Jae Joon picked it up.

558
00:47:09,977 --> 00:47:11,317
I think they are together.

559
00:47:11,317 --> 00:47:13,047
