00:52:10,437 --> 00:52:14,037
Then is your mother still there?

624
00:52:14,957 --> 00:52:17,227
You are asking me many strange questions.

625
00:52:17,227 --> 00:52:19,157
Did I?

626
00:52:19,777 --> 00:52:23,627
Would you mind if I ask your father's name?

627
00:52:23,627 --> 00:52:25,387
I want to know who he was.

628
00:52:25,387 --> 00:52:29,427
In truth, there aren't that many skillful thoracic surgeons even worldwide.

629
00:52:29,427 --> 00:52:34,527
If he's someone who raised someone like you, I was wondering if per chance I might know him as well.

630
00:52:37,937 --> 00:52:40,457
His name is Park Chul.

631
00:52:40,457 --> 00:52:42,347
Is that enough?

632
00:52:44,447 --> 00:52:46,277
Who?

633
00:52:49,797 --> 00:52:51,487
Yeah, you arrived?

