00:52:54,667 --> 00:52:57,757
Sorry, sorry. I'll be out soon.

636
00:53:22,907 --> 00:53:26,707
 How is Park Hoon's mother here?

637
00:53:26,707 --> 00:53:29,897
 I am soon going to let her meet with Park Hoon.

638
00:53:32,807 --> 00:53:34,627
Why?

639
00:53:35,487 --> 00:53:37,947
It's the Prime Minister's order.

640
00:53:46,727 --> 00:53:49,777
Why was he so curious about someone else's family history?

641
00:53:49,777 --> 00:53:51,417
Family history?

642
00:53:51,417 --> 00:53:53,197
Who?

643
00:53:54,367 --> 00:53:57,577
It's nothing, so just drive.

644
00:54:23,447 --> 00:54:25,377
 How was your father's wedding?

645
00:54:25,377 --> 00:54:29,947
 Not bad, but now I have a stepmother who is two years younger than me.

646
00:54:29,947 --> 00:54:32,757
 I have a favor to ask.

647
00:54:32,757 --> 00:54:34,677
 What is it?

648
00:54:35,437 --> 00:54:38,007
 It's about Professor Park Chul.

649
00:54:38,007 --> 00:54:39,637
 Didn't you say he went missing?

650
00:54:39,637 --> 00:54:42,067
 Find out if he went to North Korea, by any chance.

651
00:54:42,067 --> 00:54:43,817
 North Korea?

652
00:54:44,567 --> 00:54:47,247
 Work pertaining to there is costly...

653
00:54:47,247 --> 00:54:48,907
 I'll compensate for it.

654
00:54:48,907 --> 00:54:50,667
 Compensate?

655
00:54:52,027 --> 00:54:55,237
 Okay. I'll find out and call you back.

656
00:55:13,997 --> 00:55:16,587
 Are you still waiting for Professor Park Chul?

