00:55:40,197 --> 00:55:42,667
 You said you would tell them that my dad died a wrongful death.

663
00:55:42,667 --> 00:55:44,847
 You said you would testify!

664
00:55:44,847 --> 00:55:47,367
 - Seung Hoon.
